nodes.text: A rebel technician served under Commander Jun Sato as part of Phoenix Cell during the Early rebellion against the Galactic Empire. Around 4 BBY, the officer participated in the Attack on Phoenix Squadron. The technician told Sato that a ship was coming in. After losing Phoenix One and Phoenix Two, the Phoenix Home lost its hyperdrive to Darth Vader, forcing Sato and the rest of the crew to retreat.
He is voiced by Dee Bradley Baker.
